</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="180" pageNumber="783" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="180.[1364,2571,2180,2924]" pageId="180" pageNumber="783">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1366,1714,2736,2765]" pageId="180" pageNumber="783">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The [UCN Red List. The Nepalese Field Mouse is considered endangered as result ofloss of its habitat.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
